<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Bienvenido a Legalo</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
</head>
<body class="body-bg">
  <style>
    body.body-bg {
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #2d3748;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

  .main-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
  }

  .card {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      max-width: 768px;
      width: 100%;
  }

  .header {
      background-color: #000000;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 16px 24px;
      border-top-left-radius: 8px;
      border-top-right-radius: 8px;
  }

  .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
  }

  .main-content {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 24px;
  }

  .column {
      flex: 1;
      padding-right: 16px;
  }

  .title {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .description {
      color: #4a5568;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .button-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .confirm-button {
      background-color: #3182ce;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
  }

  .confirm-button:hover {
      background-color: #2c5282;
  }

  .icon {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
  }

  .image-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .image {
      max-width: 100%;
      border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .footer {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
      border-bottom-right-radius: 8px;
  }

  .footer-title {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .footer-description {
      color: #4a5568;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .contact-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
      justify-content: center;
  }

  .contact-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
  }

  .whatsapp-icon {
      color: #48bb78;
  }

  .phone-icon {
      color: #4299e1;
  }

  .contact-title {
      font-weight: bold;
  }

  .contact-detail {
      color: #718096;
  }

  .footer-note {
      color: #a0aec0;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 16px;
  }

  </style>
    <div class="main-container">
        <!-- Main Container -->
        <div class="card">
            <!-- Header -->
            <header class="header">
                <img src="https://legalo.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/legalo-logo.png" alt="Legalo Logo" />
            </header>

            <!-- Body -->
            <main class="main-content">
                <!-- Column 1 -->
                <div class="column">
                    <h2 class="title">Hola, {{ nombres }}:</h2>
                    <p class="description">
                        Toca el botón a continuación para confirmar tu correo electrónico.
                    </p>
                    <div class="button-container">
                        <a href="{{ linkActivacion }}">
                            <button class="confirm-button">
                                Confirmar correo electrónico
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="icon">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5l6 6m0 0l-6 6m6-6H3" />
                                </svg>
                            </button>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <p class="expiration-text">
                        Este enlace expirará en {{ tiempoExpiracion }} horas, así que por favor asegúrate de validarlo dentro del plazo.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </main>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <footer class="footer">
                <h3 class="footer-title">Estamos listos para ayudarte</h3>
                <p class="footer-description">Si tienes alguna duda o necesitas ayuda, contáctanos por:</p>
                <div class="contact-container">
                    <!-- WhatsApp -->
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="icon whatsapp-icon">
                            <path d="M12.05 2a10.002..."></path>
                        </svg>
                        <div>
                            <p class="contact-title">WhatsApp</p>
                            <p class="contact-detail">+123456789</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Phone -->
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="icon phone-icon">
                            <path d="M20.85 17.74c..."></path>
                        </svg>
                        <div>
                            <p class="contact-title">Llámanos al</p>
                            <p class="contact-detail">987654321</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="footer-note">
                    © 2024 Legalo Web. Todos los derechos reservados.
                </p>
            </footer>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
